Subject: Selling Your Work At A Renaissance Faire
Description: Have you thought about having your own Renaissance Festival booth? We took the plunge and built a booth at GLMF last summer and we're building a second one this year, Forsooth! come and partake of what we've learned, share your own ren booth experiences, we'll answer as many of your questions as we can.  Speakers include:Valerie Hibbard - Track: Life  - Duration: 1 hour
